FBIS4-16002 "drsov071_g_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-071 Daily Report 12 Apr 1994 WESTERN REGION Belarus Committee Deems NATO Air Attacks on Serbs `Aggression' Committee Deems NATO Air Attacks on Serbs `Aggression' WS1204200394 Minsk Radio Minsk Network in Belarusian 1715 GMT 12 Apr 94 WS1204200394 Minsk Radio Minsk Network Belarusian BFN [Text] Today, the Belarusian Committee of Solidarity With Serbs and Montenegrins held a session at the Belarusian Academy of Sciences. In connection with NATO bombing attacks on Serbian positions, the Committee, which includes well-known activists of science and culture, estimate this as an act of aggression and protests against such actions. Committee members adopted an appropriate resolution.
